{"word":"ἀναστενάζω","slug":"ἀναστενάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναστενάζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:ἀναστένω'><el>ἀναστένω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <el>τοιάδ' ἀνεστέναζες ἐχθοδοπά</el> such hateful words <i>didst thou groan forth</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to groan for, lament</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}